gtkterm2 (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add color name comments to config file output
  * Fix color reset bug (empty match string matching everything)
  * Fix color parsing (use strncmp instead of strstr)
  * Fix deprecated g_string_sprintf warning
  * Add -r/--no-rc-write command line option
  * Switch to external gettext (add gettext build dependency)
  * Update autotools files to modern versions
  * Bump version to 0.3.0

